389
00:31:38,229 --> 00:31:40,899
Kaya nagkukunwari ka lang
hindi ka marunong magsinungaling kanina?

390
00:31:42,275 --> 00:31:44,652
Wow, Kim Geon-woo. Ito ay bago.

391
00:31:44,736 --> 00:31:46,696
